shared_model

Class Field

  • java.lang.Object
    • shared_model.Field

  • public class Field
extends java.lang.Object
    A column for values in a project. Has a name, xCoord and id to link it to its parent project. Also contains the ID linking it to its corresponding batch.
    Author:
    jchip May 2015
